{"tid":1738191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰術】改變防守心態 要進攻","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:26:40.000Z","uid":144433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95bf9e5b55eeb5ec36b565f04873e1b327dc76a5","tid":1738191,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"前線 盾兵包圍住魔法師 不斷向前行<br />\n當進攻時 前面盾兵左右散開<br />\n然後不斷向前推進<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HcWJMudcIxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHcWJMudcIxo&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=f6bc6d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HcWJMudcIxo</a>"},{"pid":"b8aab4b0d4e9d72e4d894d4555b225a76b9650e3","tid":1738191,"uid":63336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"心態比陣式重要<br />\n不過人地尋晚用高速突破"},{"pid":"fc3ec204bde34decb1e2bcd20f0ffa98d9e2fd1a","tid":1738191,"uid":75879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"不要迷戀與狗博鬥 要做返多啲爭取民主大局上嘅事 如每星期一次嘅和理非遊行<br />\n不建議陣地 但兩軍對壘時 只有專雨才是救贖<br />\n前排搵嘢擋 越大件越好<br />\n後排不斷傅專上前 邊推進邊出專雨<br />\n一定要推進不要企定定 否則會變晒煙燻魚<br />\n專不要太大件 會影響射程<br />\n大量專雨落地後 會化成專陣 可阻水車銳武前進<br />\n火魔射程太近及量少珍貴 只有狗衝個時用嚟做屏障 不要亂放<br />\n好人一生平安 認同請勿廣傳"},{"pid":"0fd4fc4f6f5b6cb6ecc9f5d420b6c0616c47703b","tid":1738191,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:26:40.000Z","msg":"自製防彈衣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738137</a>"}]}